These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
Food: peas, lettuce, spinach, grapefruit
Nationality: malaysian, canadian, spanish, nigerian
1. Nationality:canadian is on the left of Nationality:malaysian##1
2. Food:peas == Nationality:nigerian##1
3. Nationality:spanish is on the right of Nationality:malaysian##1
4. Food:lettuce is on the left of Nationality:nigerian##1
5. Food:grapefruit is on the left of Nationality:malaysian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Food          | grapefruit | spinach | lettuce | peas   |
| Nationality   | canadian  | malaysian     | spanish   | nigerian |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
Hobby: collecting, puzzles, skydiving, singing
Sport: lacrosse, surfing, skiing, ice-hockey
1. Hobby:singing == Sport:surfing##1
2. Hobby:collecting is on the far right##1
3. Hobby:puzzles is on the right of Hobby:singing##1
4. Hobby:singing is on the right of Sport:skiing##1
5. Sport:surfing is on the left of Sport:lacrosse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby   | skydiving | singing | puzzles | collecting    |
| Sport   | skiing    | surfing      | lacrosse | ice-hockey |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-3::.
