3. Movie-Genre:satire is on the far right##1
4. Movie-Genre:thriller is on the right of Hobby:dancing##1
5. Hobby:drawing is on the left of Movie-Genre:satire##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3      |       4       |
| Hobby         | hiking | dancing | drawing   | filmmaking |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy   | scientific | thriller | satire         |

