.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-11::.
Beverage: iced-tea, almond-milk, 7up, coffee
Music-Genre: funk, house, indie, techno
1. Music-Genre:indie is on the right of Music-Genre:funk##1
2. Music-Genre:techno is on the right of Music-Genre:indie##1
3. Beverage:coffee is on the right of Beverage:iced-tea##1
4. Beverage:7up is on the far left##1
5. Beverage:almond-milk == Music-Genre:indie##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |       3       |   4   |
| Beverage      | 7up | almond-milk  | iced-tea | coffee |
| Music-Genre   | funk  | indie | techno           | house   |

