.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-20::.
Nationality: french, italian, malaysian, thai
Transport: jet-ski, train, motorbike, taxi
1. Transport:jet-ski is on the left of Nationality:italian##1
2. Transport:train is on the left of Nationality:thai##1
3. Nationality:french is on the left of Nationality:malaysian##1
4. Nationality:thai == Transport:taxi##1
5. Transport:jet-ski is on the left of Nationality:italian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Nationality   | french | malaysian | italian | thai   |
| Transport     | motorbike  | jet-ski    | train       | taxi |

 